{
  "info": {
    "name": "Ticketing System API Tests",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - Login Admin",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ticketing.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Get My Tickets (Bearer Token)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickets/my",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "tickets", "my"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "03 - Create Ticket",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Postman Test Ticket\",\n  \"description\": \"Testing API endpoints\",\n  \"priority\": \"MEDIUM\",\n  \"category\": \"BUG\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickets",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "tickets"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "04 - Admin: Get All Users",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/users",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "admin", "users"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "05 - Register New User",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test{{ $randomUUID }}@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"test123\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Test User\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  }
}

## 🚀 **HOW TO USE** (Import to Postman)

1. **Import** POSTMAN_TESTS.json
2. **Set base_url**: `http://localhost:8080` (local) or Render URL
3. **Run 01-Login** → Copy token from response → Paste in `token` environment var
4. **Run 02-05** → Tests complete flow

**Expected**: No 403s, login works, tickets CRUD ✓

**Test Credentials**:
- Admin: `admin@ticketing.com` / `admin123`
- Agent: `agent@ticketing.com` / `agent123`
- User: `user@ticketing.com` / `user123`
